label.value: floor material role

definition.value: A building material role that inheres in a material entity that is realized in a building process in which the material entity will become part of a floor.

label.value: obsolete dwelling facility role

definition.value: A role that inheres in a material entity that is realized in a process that provides a convenience or service to people who are living in a dwelling.

label.value: obsolete organismal body temperature measurement datum

definition.value: A temperature measurement datum that is about an organism.

label.value: obsolete floor brick

definition.value: A processed material shaped a small rectangular block typically made of clay mixed with sand and fired in a kiln or baked by the sun, used in building floor construction.

label.value: obsolete age since birth at time of visit

definition.value: An age since birth measurement datum at the time of a clinical visit.

label.value: average asexual parasite density of a participant with asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia

definition.value: An average value of asexual parasites counted per microliter of blood (i.e. malaria parasite density) across mulitiple clinical visits of a participant who was diagnosed with asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia.

label.value: average asexual parasite density of a participant with malaria

definition.value: An average value of asexual parasites counted per microliter of blood (i.e. malaria parasite density) across mulitiple clinical visits of a participant who was diagnosed with malaria.

label.value: average number of female Anopheles per night

definition.value: An average value of female Anopheles mosquitoes collected across multiple collections (e.g. from one or more households on a number of nights).

label.value: average number of female Anopheles tested for sporozoite

definition.value: An average value of Anopheles mosquitoes tested for sporozoites across multiple collections (e.g. from a given household across CDC light trap collections) in a given period.

label.value: average number of sporozoite-positive female Anopheles

definition.value: An average value of sporozoite positive female Anopheles mosquitoes across multiple collections (e.g. from a given household over a number of nights of collections).

label.value: average percent of female Anopheles with Plasmodium sporozoites

definition.value: An average percentage value of female Anopheles mosquitoes tested as sporozoites-positive in all female mosquitoes tested for sporozoites across multiple collections.

label.value: obsolete age since birth at time of enrollment

definition.value: An age since birth measurement datum at the time of subject enrollment.

label.value: number of clinical visits

definition.value: A data item of the total number of clinical visits by a participant in an investigation.

label.value: number of clinical visits resulting in a malaria diagnosis

definition.value: A data item of the number of clinical visits during which the participant was diagnosed with malaria

label.value: number of clinical visits resulting in an asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia diagnosis

definition.value: A data item of the number of clinical visits during which the participant was diagnosed with asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia.

label.value: obsolete number of non-routine clinical visits

definition.value: A data item of the total number of clinical visits which were not sheduled routine visits.

label.value: obsolete number of routine clinical visits

definition.value: A data item of the total number of clinical visits which were not sheduled routine visits.

label.value: obsolete sample available information

definition.value: An information content entity that is about the type of sample/specimen collected during a clinical visit.

label.value: obsolete blood specimen on filter paper

definition.value: A blood specimen that is located on a filter paper.

label.value: peripheral blood mononuclear cell specimen

definition.value: A processed specimen that is extracted from whole blood using gradient centrifugation that separates the blood into a layer of peripheral blood mononuclear cell under the top layer of plasma. It contains lymphocytes, monocytes or macrophages that are critical components in the immune system.

label.value: obsolete red blood cell specimen

definition.value: A processed specimen consisting of red blood cells isolated from whole blood by centrifugation.

label.value: obsolete average number of Plasmodium parasite-positive female Anopheles

definition.value: An average value for female Anopheles mosquitoes tested positive for carrying Plasmodium parasites across multiple collections (e.g. from a given household across CDC light trap collections) in a given period.

label.value: obsolete average number of female Anopheles tested for Plasmodium parasite

definition.value: An average value for female Anopheles mosquitoes tested for carrying Plasmodium parasites across multiple collections (e.g. from a given household across CDC light trap collections) in a given period.

label.value: obsolete average percent of Plasmodium parasite-positive female Anopheles

definition.value: An average percentage value for female Anopheles mosquitoes carrying Plasmodium parasites in all female mosquitoes tested for carrying Plasmodium parasites across multiple collections.

label.value: number of Anopheles collections

definition.value: A count of Anopheles mosquitoes collections performed (e.g. from a given household) in a given period.

label.value: sum number of female Anopheles in a collection

definition.value: A sum value for all species of female Anopheles mosquitoes in a given collections.

label.value: sum number of female Anopheles funestus in a collection

definition.value: A sum value for all female Anopheles funestus mosquitoes in a given collections.

label.value: sum number of female Anopheles gambiae in a collection

definition.value: A sum value for all female Anopheles gambiae mosquitoes in a given collections.

label.value: duration of observation of study participant

definition.value: A time datum for the duration of a patients participation in an investigation.

label.value: average number of clinical visits per year

definition.value: An average value for the number of clinical visits of a patient based on calendar years

label.value: average number of clinical visits with asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia diagnosis per year

definition.value: An average value for the number of clinical visits of a patient with asymptomatic microscopic parasitemia based on calendar years.

label.value: average number of clinical visits with malaria diagnosis per year

definition.value: An average value for the number of clinical visits of a patient with malaria based on calendar years

label.value: obsolete routine clinical visit date

definition.value: A clinical visit date that specifies the date/time period of a routine clinical visit.

label.value: categorical household wealth index

definition.value: A data item about a household's cumulative living standard represented in a categorical datum. The wealth index is calculated using data on a household's ownership of selected assets, such as televisions and bicycles; materials used for housing construction; and types of water access and sanitation facilities.

label.value: household asset information

definition.value: An information content entity about items that a household owns such as a car, funiture, etc.

label.value: obsolete antimalarial therapy given outside the study since last seen information

definition.value: An information content entity indicating whether a person was given antimalarial therapy outside the study since last seen as part of the study.

label.value: obsolete cause of participant death

definition.value: An information content entity indicating the cause of death for a participant in the study.

label.value: obsolete clinical visit when sick

definition.value: A clinical visit occuring because of a sickness.

label.value: obsolete covered pit latrine without slab

definition.value: A covered pit latrine that does not have a latrine slab.

label.value: date of death

definition.value: A time measurement datum specifying the date of death

label.value: date of participant first enrolled in a study

definition.value: A time measurement datum that specified the date of participant first enrolled in a study

label.value: date of participant last seen in a study

definition.value: A time measurement datum that specified the date of participant last seen in a study

label.value: obsolete days since a clinical visit with a malaria diagnosis

definition.value: A time measurement datum measuring the number of days since a clinical visit took place which resulted in a malaria diagnosis.

label.value: duration of abdominal pain

definition.value: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having abdominal pain.

label.value: duration of anorexia

definition.value: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having anorexia.

label.value: duration of cough

definition.value: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having a cough.

label.value: duration of diarrhea

definition.value: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having diarrhea.

label.value: duration of fatigue

definition.value: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having fatigue.

label.value: duration of headache

definition.value: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having a headache.

label.value: duration of jaundice

definition.value: A time measurement datum that measures the duration of having jaundice.
